  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<div style="overflow: hidden; position: relative;"><img style="float: right; margin-left: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 75px; height: auto;" src="https://www.inghams.co.uk/media/13108757/inghams-choice-light-1.png" alt="Inghams Choice" />
<p>Chalet Chloe is one three Inghams chalets in a small residence just by the Balcons area of Val Thorens with a 100 metres walk connecting to the Plein Sud piste. This chalet has four bedrooms and is ideal for a small group of family or friends. Offered on a chalet catering board basis, you'll enjoy breakfast, afternoon tea and cakes, dinner and wine included with your stay. This chalet sleeps 8-10 people and can be booked for sole occupancy.</p>
</div>]]></listingDescription>
